{"tid":1024987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年全球軍費支出排行榜出爐 中國躍居第二","createTime":"2019-02-17T04:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T05:28:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d71e534230237d8f8b52e9850a4bedb7891862","tid":1024987,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.iiss.org/-/media/images/comment/military-balance-blog/2019/february/mb2019-defence-budgets-1-online-866px.ashx?la=en&amp;hash=AB1826AE04322F84599E07CA4248E0D24A5B450B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iiss.org%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcomment%2Fmilitary-balance-blog%2F2019%2Ffebruary%2Fmb2019-defence-budgets-1-online-866px.ashx%3Fla%3Den%26hash%3DAB1826AE04322F84599E07CA4248E0D24A5B450B&h=4383db84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據IISS統計數據顯示，2018年全球武器和國防支出在去年成長了1.8%，超過1.67兆美元，其中近半數成長來自美國。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-17 10:46<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕2018年全球軍費支出排行榜出爐，排名第1的國家為美國，軍費支出費用為6433億美元（約新台幣19.8兆）。而緊追在後的中國，去年軍事支出費用為1682億美元（約新台幣5.2兆）。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，IISS統計報告認為，中國欲實現其2035年軍事現代化的計畫，近年積極發展軍事研究，也讓該國軍事逐年上升。據IISS統計數據顯示，中國軍事支出從2016年1437億美元、2017年的1484美元至2018年國防開支增長至1682美元，這讓一直視中國為戰略競爭對手的美國感到憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n而為保持美國對中國的軍力優勢，美國在2018年增加軍費開支，至6433億美元。據統計數據顯示，全球武器和國防支出在去年成長了1.8%，超過1.67兆美元（約新台幣51.45兆），其中有近半數的成長來自美國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去的軍事大國俄羅斯，在去年的軍費支出僅有631億美元（約新台幣1.9兆），不到美國10分之1。但有觀察家提出警告，表示俄羅斯的軍事影響力遠超於歐洲，要歐洲各國千萬不能因為俄羅斯軍費開支的相對較少，而縮減該國的軍費費用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2701231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701231&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2FE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=bcdf72e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701231&h=765fef4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2701231</a>"},{"pid":"8ff98b2951a9327c0a4ef123825819fe748094ad","tid":1024987,"uid":79655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"高支出又唔代表啲乜<br />\n<br />\n中國夠多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fca8b9745bbd2b76dc0cf23860122e14a24fd98","tid":1024987,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"中共政治局委員楊潔篪的表態，是重申北京的一貫立場。他說，中國的軍力只用於自衛，不威脅任何國家。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb84b0fad6bbccbdc2e97bd28885cba8ab9d6815","tid":1024987,"uid":182927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff98b2951a9327c0a4ef123825819fe748094ad","tid":1024987,"uid":79655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"高支出又唔代表啲乜<br />\n<br />\n中國夠多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"唔claim大條數，點落自己袋?"},{"pid":"a31cd9143d5fad52bfa52954594621cda1dd8524","tid":1024987,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ff98b2951a9327c0a4ef123825819fe748094ad","tid":1024987,"uid":79655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"高支出又唔代表啲乜<br />\n<br />\n中國夠多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"討厭佢但唔好輕視佢"},{"pid":"dda7750f103a4209e5b42df1b6284b78416f4ae4","tid":1024987,"uid":118910,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"其實香港根本有錢有資源可以建立自己軍隊<br />\n平時幾多錢掉落d垃圾大笨象<br />\n高鐵 三跑 大愚 加埋都兆幾兩兆港紙<br />\n換番轉bn美金再變番每年開支已經可以媲美普通國家國防開支"},{"pid":"0433c82a633e948ab71b587326b609a5ee236187","tid":1024987,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:12:26.